        {
            "id": 6010162,
            "title": "宏達電5月營收重返2億大關月增近4成 VR海外布局有所斬獲",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>VR 軟硬體整合商宏達電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2498:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2498\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2498-TW</a>) 今 (6) 日公告 5 月營收為 2.19 億元，重返 2 億元大關，呈年月雙增；累積前 5 月營收達 10.84 億元，年增逾 13%；宏達電近期布局 VR 海外市場頗有斬獲，與美國德州大學奧斯汀分校合作，跨入虛擬教育領域。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010162%2Fl%2Ff59b70c5742c86a2424372b5eac0b5aa.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010162%2Fl%2Ff59b70c5742c86a2424372b5eac0b5aa.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010162%2Fl%2Ff59b70c5742c86a2424372b5eac0b5aa.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010162%2Fl%2Ff59b70c5742c86a2424372b5eac0b5aa.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010162%2Fl%2Ff59b70c5742c86a2424372b5eac0b5aa.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010162%2Fl%2Ff59b70c5742c86a2424372b5eac0b5aa.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010162%2Fl%2Ff59b70c5742c86a2424372b5eac0b5aa.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010162%2Fl%2Ff59b70c5742c86a2424372b5eac0b5aa.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010162%2Fl%2Ff59b70c5742c86a2424372b5eac0b5aa.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010162%2Fl%2Ff59b70c5742c86a2424372b5eac0b5aa.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010162%2Fl%2Ff59b70c5742c86a2424372b5eac0b5aa.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010162%2Fl%2Ff59b70c5742c86a2424372b5eac0b5aa.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010162%2Fl%2Ff59b70c5742c86a2424372b5eac0b5aa.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010162%2Fl%2Ff59b70c5742c86a2424372b5eac0b5aa.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010162%2Fl%2Ff59b70c5742c86a2424372b5eac0b5aa.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010162%2Fl%2Ff59b70c5742c86a2424372b5eac0b5aa.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010162%2Fl%2Ff59b70c5742c86a2424372b5eac0b5aa.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">宏達電5月營收重返2億大關月增近4成 VR海外布局有所斬獲。(圖：shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>宏達電 2025 年 5 月營收 2.19 億元，月增 39.39%，年增 14.64%；累計前 5 月營業收入 10.84 億元，年增 13.04%。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>宏達電旗下致力於打造 3D Internet 虛擬世界 VIVERSE 首度攜手美國德州大學奧斯汀分校，與其傳播學院德州沉浸式研究院（Texas Immersive Institute）展開為期一學期的深度合作，正式將無需編碼、可跨平台操作的 VIVERSE Create 平台導入課程，推動 WebXR 3D 創作進入美國大學教室。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>另外，宏達電與光寶科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2301:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2301\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2301-TW</a>) 於 2025 COMPUTEX 展會聯合展示最新 5G 專網解決方案。展出內容包括採用 G REIGNS 自主開發的 5G vRAN 架構，結合符合業界標準的 5GC 核心網技術與光寶科技 O-RU 設備，支援 Sub-6GHz 頻段，可實現端到端的專網建置，未來可應用於智慧工廠等場域。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
